Josephine Tewson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Josephine_Tewson 0 Josephine Ann Tewson (born 26 February 1931) is an English stage and television actress. She is best known for her large roles in British television sitcoms, such as Elizabeth "Liz" Warden the neighbour of Hyacinth Bucket in Keeping Up Appearances (1990–95) and Miss Davenport in Last of the Summer Wine (2003–10).
